article_title: Political Uncertainty Will Continue To Stunt Economic Growth

article_metadata.description: I's the uncertainty, stupid. Moody’s Analytics chief economist Mark Zandi says Washington’s continuing budget and debt wars are the biggest threat to economic growth.
article_metadata.author: Janet Novack
